				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/C%E1%BA%ADn-hoa/poem--LqZ-26yvUutH5unXxBceQ">Cận hoa - 槿花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/C%E1%BB%91-kinh-thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-Bnkkrx7E3qXhFqYmPe010A">Cố kinh thu nhật - 故京秋日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/C%E1%BB%ADu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BA%A5t-nh%E1%BA%ADt-qu%C3%A1-M%E1%BA%A1nh-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%C3%A0o-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-th%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%A9-ch%E1%BB%A7-b%E1%BA%A1-huynh-%C4%91%E1%BB%87/poem-N50q6f-0icrKz_EiERi1sQ">Cửu nguyệt nhất nhật quá Mạnh thập nhị tào trưởng, thập tứ chủ bạ huynh đệ - 九月一日過孟十二倉曹、十四主簿兄弟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/%C4%90i%E1%BB%83m-gi%C3%A1ng-th%E1%BA%A7n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-CfESL2c9KCPDBpriNFoxMw">Điểm giáng thần kỳ 2 - 點絳脣其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-6q8syMJi1LKPt3rH8HfbQQ">Lý Thanh Chiếu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/L%E1%BB%A5c-ti%C3%AAu-4/poem-OenkUkdt6jHp1mm6ZEZruQ">Lục tiêu 4 - 蓼蕭 4</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Ph%C3%A0m-th%C3%A1nh-b%E1%BA%A5t-d%E1%BB%8B/poem-PlXA0GB-oGcJapEpaNVdyA">Phàm thánh bất dị - 凡聖不異</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BA%A1i-ng%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-thi%E1%BB%81n/poem-LvAgfE08bW_GHmspFhIapQ">Tại ngục vịnh thiền - 在獄詠蟬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-jvbfrjspi2Y6S8b3jeqzpA">Lạc Tân Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chung-Tinh/Thu-hi%E1%BB%83u/poem-lzHwSoxY1qciUrNggS1E3g">Thu hiểu - 秋曉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chung-Tinh/author-u6-RIhUvEY9JL42vswhrag">Chung Tinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C5%A9-S%C6%A1n-v%C5%A9-b%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1c-n%C3%AA/poem-Jh0ybTlYkxJlmL_djGuRGg">Vũ (Sơn vũ bất tác nê) - 雨（山雨不作泥）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%91c-b%E1%BA%AFc-vi%C3%AAn-t%C3%A2n-du%E1%BA%A9n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-NxQ-6dr6Iu5leqASYW1MlQ">Xương Cốc bắc viên tân duẩn kỳ 2 - 昌谷北園新筍其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/author-6YXs2qoM-0pPFaxDDrLTew">Lý Hạ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
